'''[[relative]] [[humidity]]'''
# the [[ratio]] of the [[absolute humidity]] (vapor pressure) to the [[maximum]] [[possible]] humidity at the same [[temperature]] (saturation vapor pressure) - often expressed as a [[percentage]] - which may be calculated from [[psychrometric]] data.

